User - User Role
----------------
 PatientInfo - TreatmentPlan - Appointment - Department - MedicalRecord

treatment plan -> Tedavi Planı
Patient Info -> Hasta Bilgisi
Appointment  -> Randevu
MedicalRecord ->
Department ->


Entities and Relationships:
---------------------
Doctor:
    OneToOne: UserRole
    OneToMany: PatientInfo, Appointment
    ManyToMany: TreatmentPlan
Nurse:
    OneToOne: UserRole
    OneToMany: PatientInfo, Appointment
    ManyToMany: TreatmentPlan
Patient:
    OneToOne: UserRole
    OneToMany: TreatmentPlan, Appointment
Manager:
    OneToOne: UserRole
    OneToMany: PatientInfo, Appointment
    ManyToMany: TreatmentPlan
Admin:
    OneToOne: UserRole
    OneToMany: PatientInfo, Appointment
    ManyToMany: TreatmentPlan
Patient - Info
    OneToOne: PatientInfo (reverse relationship)
Treatment Plan - Appointment
    ManyToOne: Appointment (reverse relationship)

